#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.asarray.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.asarray"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:1 of
msgid "Convert the input to an array."
msgstr "将输入转换为数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:3 of
msgid ""
"Input data, in any form that can be converted to a tensor.  This includes"
" lists, lists of tuples, tuples, tuples of tuples, tuples of lists and "
"tensors."
msgstr ""
"输入数据，可以是任何能够转换为张量的形式。这包括列表、元组列表、元组、"
"元组的元组、列表的元组以及张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:7 of
msgid "By default, the data-type is inferred from the input data."
msgstr "默认情况下，数据类型从输入数据中推断得出。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:9 of
msgid ""
"Whether to use row-major (C-style) or column-major (Fortran-style) memory"
" representation."
msgstr "是否使用行主序（C 风格）或列主序（Fortran 风格）的内存表示方式。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:12 of
msgid "Specifies chunk size for each dimension."
msgstr "指定每个维度的块大小。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:15 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Tensor interpretation of `a`.  No copy is performed if the "
"input is already an ndarray with matching dtype and order.  If `a` is a "
"subclass of ndarray, a base class ndarray is returned."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- `a` 的张量解释。如果输入已经是具有匹配数据类型和顺序的 ndarray"
"，则不执行复制操作。如果 `a` 是 ndarray 的子类，则返回基类 ndarray。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ascontiguousarray`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:23 of
msgid "Convert input to a contiguous tensor."
msgstr "将输入转换为连续张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`asfortranarray`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:26 of
msgid "Convert input to a tensor with column-major memory order."
msgstr "将输入转换为以列主序内存顺序存储的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:29 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:30 of
msgid "Convert a list into a tensor:"
msgstr "将列表转换为张量："

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:38 of
msgid "Existing arrays are not copied:"
msgstr "现有数组不会被复制："

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.array.asarray:44 of
msgid "If `dtype` is set, array is copied only if dtype does not match:"
msgstr "如果设置了 `dtype`，仅在数据类型不匹配时才复制数组："

